  {
    "chunk_id": "docling_newspaper_d7fe1132386670993aae3dabc6247bc9_2_9",
    "text": "Proposed Information Collection; Comment Request; Benchmark Survey of Insurance Transactions by U.S. Insurance Companies with Foreign Persons",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
      0.0714285734022556,
      0.2223837208256656,
      0.34774435873623166,
      0.28343023225493963
    ],
    "page": "newspaper_d7fe1132386670993aae3dabc6247bc9_2",
    "order": 14
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "docling_newspaper_d7fe1132386670993aae3dabc6247bc9_2_19",
    "text": "The data are needed to monitor U.S. international trade in insurance services, analyze its impact on the U.S. economy and foreign economies, compile and improve the U.S. economic accounts, support U.S. commercial policy on insurance services, conduct trade promotion, and improve the ability of U.S. businesses to identify and evaluate market opportunities.",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
      0.3590225529370301,
      0.2266865077384859,
      0.6353383424918589,
      0.3531976741106808
    ],
    "page": "newspaper_d7fe1132386670993aae3dabc6247bc9_2",
    "order": 15
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "docling_newspaper_d7fe1132386670993aae3dabc6247bc9_2_10",
    "text": "AGENCY: Bureau of Economic Analysis, Commerce.",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
      0.07329100336660832,
      0.29215116280119857,
      0.33834585715132803,
      0.31548559885891253
    ],
    "page": "newspaper_d7fe1132386670993aae3dabc6247bc9_2",
    "order": 16
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "docling_newspaper_d7fe1132386670993aae3dabc6247bc9_2_11",
    "text": "ACTION: Notice.",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
      0.07142857150375942,
      0.31820436497055365,
      0.17669172939849623,
      0.3313953487504002
    ],
    "page": "newspaper_d7fe1132386670993aae3dabc6247bc9_2",
    "order": 17
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "docling_newspaper_d7fe1132386670993aae3dabc6247bc9_2_12",
    "text": "SUMMARY: The Department of Commerce, as part of its continuing effort to reduce paperwork and respondent burden, invites the general public and other Federal agencies to comment on proposed and/or continuing information collections, as required by the Paperwork Reduction Act of 1995.",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
      0.07142856996615747,
      0.33854166662799656,
      0.3364661645989975,
      0.45240831554695826
    ],
    "page": "newspaper_d7fe1132386670993aae3dabc6247bc9_2",
    "order": 18
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "docling_newspaper_d7fe1132386670993aae3dabc6247bc9_2_18",
    "text": "This survey is conducted at five year intervals; it was last conducted for 2008 and will be conducted again for 2013. The 2013 survey will be sent to respondents on March 30, 2014 and reports are due by June 30, 2014.",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
      0.36090225527599856,
      0.3516865081257513,
      0.6334586434552046,
      0.4288194443349324
    ],
    "page": "newspaper_d7fe1132386670993aae3dabc6247bc9_2",
    "order": 19
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "docling_newspaper_d7fe1132386670993aae3dabc6247bc9_2_20",
    "text": "Two changes are proposed to the 2013 BE-140 form: (1) drop questions on finite reinsurance because finite reinsurance is a dated concept that is no longer relevant, and (2) add questions to identify the transaction code, size, type and nature of large and irregular transactions, defined as those contracts with premiums ceded or assumed in excess of $1 billion and that are at least three times the size of a reporter's average regular contract. The new information will allow BEA to measure more accurately insurance services on an accrual basis and to exclude transactions that are not related to insurance services.",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
      0.36090225271490833,
      0.42732558126655706,
      0.6372180458753173,
      0.6396329364787668
    ],
    "page": "newspaper_d7fe1132386670993aae3dabc6247bc9_2",
    "order": 20
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "docling_newspaper_d7fe1132386670993aae3dabc6247bc9_2_35",
    "text": "Dated: July 30, 2013.",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
